rministic $k$-OBDDs using our\nlower bounds for $ k=o(n/ \\log n)$. We also analyze similar hierarchies for\nsuperpolynomial and subexponential width $k$-OBDDs.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 19 Dec 2016 09:46:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-12-20"}
